{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Akabs Amrus Dehle\ndarrija/ kas tam KUNGAṀ ne\npatikke/ wairak ne ka wiſſi/ kas\npreekſch winna bijutchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſcham ſchkittahs\nmaſa Leeta effant eekſch Jerobena-\nma Neebata Dehla Grehkeem\nſtaigaht. Un wiꞥſch nehme Ise-\nbeli Ethaäla ta Zihdonezu Keh-\nniza Meitu par Seewu/ un gah-\nje/ un kalpoja Baälam/ un klan-\nntjahs preekſch ta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch uszehle Baä-\nlain weenn Altari Baäla Nam-\nmâ/ ko wiꞥſch eekſch Samarijas\nbij darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Akabs darrija arridsan\nkuplu Meschu/ ta ka Akabs wai-\nraſ darrija to KUNGU Israëta\nDeewu apkaitinadams / ne ka\nwiſſi Israëka Rehnizi / kas\npreekſch winna bijuschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winna Laika ustaifija\nKiëls tas Beteliteris Jeriku/ kad\ntas winna Pamattus likke / tad\ntas winnam maſaja winna\npirmdsimtu Dehlu/ un kad tas\nwinna Wahrtis eezeble/ tad mak-\nfaja tas winna maſaku Dehlu /\npehz ta KUNGA Wahrdu/ ko\nwiꞥſch runnajs zaur Josuü Nun-\nna Dehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N Elijas tas Tisbiteris\nno Gileadas Eedshwo-\ntajeeim fazzija us Akabu:\nTik teefchain ka tas KUNGS\nIsraëla Deews dshwo/ preeſch\nka es stahwu / schinnis Gaddôs\nne buhs neds Raffa neds Leetus/\nka ween kad es to fluddinaſchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta KUNGA Wahrdg\nnotikke us to/ fazzidams:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eij nobst no ſchejenes/ un\ngreesees prett Rihteem / un ap-\nfleppees pee tahs Uppes Krites/\nkas preeſch ta Jardana tekk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tur tu warri no tahs\nUppes dsert / un es efmu teem\nKrankteem paweblejs/ ka teem\ntew tur buhs usturreht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch nogahje/ un dar-\nrija pehz ta KUNGA Wahrdg/\nun gahje/un palikke pee tahs Up-\npes Krites/ kas preeſch Jarda-\nna tekk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Krankki atneffe win-\nnam Maſi/ un Galtu / Rihtds\nun Wakkardg/ un wiꞥſch dsehre\nno tahs Uppes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet pehz tahdu Laiku is-\ntike ta Uppe/ jo Leetus ne bija\ntai Semine.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ktua ta KUNGA\nWahrdg us wiꞥſchu/ fazzidans:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zellees/ un eij us Zarpa-\ntu/kas teem Zihdonezeem peederr/\nun paleez tur/ reds/ es efmu tur\nweenai Atraitnei paweblejs / ka\nwiꞥſai tew buhs usturreht.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
